# Related file: package.json (specifically `packageJson.scripts`)
#
# pre-commit commands:
# - `npm run build` - Build the codebase to lib/ so that all configuration files are up-to-date.
# - `lint-staged`   - Run the validation checks scoped to just the staged files prior to any changes being committed.
#
# Excerpt from https://github.com/lint-staged/lint-staged#command-line-flags:
# > --relative - pass filepaths relative to `process.cwd()` (where `lint-staged` runs) to tasks; default is `false`
# > --verbose  - show task output even when tasks succeed; by default only failed output is shown
npm run githooks:pre-commit
